org.eclipse.keyple.plugin.remotese.transport.model

Class KeypleDtoHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.keyple.plugin.remotese.transport.model.KeypleDtoHelper

  • public final class KeypleDtoHelper
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class to manipulate KeypleDto. Use this class to build the different types of KeypleDto
    • Request
    • Response
    • Notification
    • NoResponse
    • Exception

        Build a keypleDto of type "Exception" containing a Java Exception

        This keypleDto send the exception to the other node

        Parameters:
        action - : name of the remote method that failed
        sessionId - : virtual session id (if exists)
        nativeReaderName - : name of the local reader
        virtualReaderName - : name of the virtual reader (if exists)
        requesterNodeId - : node id of the sender
        targetNodeId - : node id of the destinee
        id - : id of the failed request
        exception - : exception that occurs during the execution of the method
        Returns:
        keypleDto of type "Exception"
